		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />It's not "easy", it requires time and patience, plus full 6502 knowledge. We have a few examples of tweaking the FDS BIOS, but nothing about replacing it. Anyway, the FDS emulation is crap, since most emulators use self-empiric things to get it working. I know a few pirated versions of FDS games "ported" into iNES format, but that's it.
<br />
